---
title: Salisbury Steaks and Onion Gravy with Creamy Mash and Roasted Broccoli
description: We're bringing back memories of grandma's kitchen with these retro hamburger steaks, smothered in onion gravy. Creamy mashed potatoes alongside are a must, while roasted broccoli finishes off the plate with a green touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1024_W10_CA_RB155673-1_Main_Low-d6922949.jpg
